{"text":"1. Alif. Laam. Ro. 
(Ushbu) kitob oyatlari mahkam qilingan, 
so`ngra hikmatli va xabardor Zot tomonidan 
mufassal (bayon) qilingandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,134]}]}

{"text":"2. Allohdan o`zgaga ibodat qilmasligingiz uchundir. Albatta, men sizlarga Undan kelgan ogohlantiruvchi va xushxabarchiman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,122]}]}

{"text":"3. Robbingizga istig`for aytinglar, \nso`ngra Unga tavba qilinglar. (Shunda) \nU zot sizlarni ma'lum muddatgacha yaxshi rohatlar ila bahramand qilur va har bir fazl egasiga fazlini berur. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,186]}]}

{"text":"Agar yuz o`girib ketsangiz, bas, albatta, men sizlarga ulug` kunning azobi bo`lishidan qo`rqaman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,97]}]}

{"text":"4. Allohning O`ziga qaytishingiz bor. \nU har bir narsaga qodir Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,70]}]}

{"text":"5. Ogoh bo`lingkim, albatta, ular Undan \nyashirinish uchun ko`ksilariga (boshlarini) egarlar. \nOgoh bo`lingkim, kiyimlariga o`ralgan chog`larida ham, U zot nimani sir tutayotganlariniyu nimani oshkor qilayotganlarini bilar. Albatta, U  qalblardagi bor narsalarni bilguvchi Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,281]}]}

{"text":"6. Yer yuzida o`rmalagan narsa borki, 
ularning rizqi Allohning zimmasidadir. 
U ularning turar joylarini ham, borar joylarini 
ham bilur. Hammasi ochiq-oydin kitobdadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"7. U sizlardan qaysingizning amali yaxshiroq ekanini sinab ko`rish uchun olti kunda osmonlaru yerni yaratdi. O`shanda Arshi suv ustida edi. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"Agar sen: Sizlar o`limdan keyin albatta qayta tiriltirilasizlar, desang, kufr keltirganlar, albatta: \nBu ochiq-oydin sehrdan o`zga narsa emas, derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,154]}]}

{"text":"8. Agar Biz ulardan ma'lum muddatgacha azobni kechiktirsak, ular albatta: Uni nima to`xtatib turibdi? derlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,112]}]}

{"text":"Ogoh bo`linglarkim, u kelgan kunda ulardan \nqaytarilmas va ularni o`zlari istehzo qilib yurgan \nnarsa o`rab olur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,113]}]}

{"text":"9. Agar insonga O`z tomonimizdan rohatni tottirib, \nso`ngra undan uni tortib olsak, u albatta noumid va noshukr bo`lur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"10. Agar unga yetgan qiyinchiliklardan so`ng ne'mat tottirsak, albatta: Mendan yomonliklar ketdi, deydi. Albatta, u xursand va faxrlidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,139]}]}

{"text":"11. Magar sabr qilganlar va yaxshi amallar qilganlar, \nana o`shalarga mag`firat va katta ajr bor.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,97]}]}

{"text":"12. Ehtimol, sen ularning: Unga xazina tushirilsa edi yoki U bilan birga farishta kelsa edi, deganlari uchun o`zingga vahiy qilingan narsaning ba'zisini tark qilmoqchi bo`larsan yoki undan yuraging siqilar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,211]}]}

{"text":"13. Yoki: O`zi to`qib oldi, derlarmi? Sen: Bas, agar rostgo`y bo`lsalaringiz, Allohdan boshqa kimni chaqirishga qodir bo`lsangiz, chaqirib, bunga \no`xshash o`nta to`qilgan sura keltiring-chi, degin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,202]}]}

{"text":"14. Agar javob bera olmasalar, bas, bilingki, \nu faqatgina Allohning ilmi ila nozil qilingandir. Undan \no`zga biron iloh yo`qdir. Endi musulmon bo`larsizlar?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,158]}]}

{"text":"15. Kimki bu dunyo hayotini va uning ziynatini xohlasa, bu boradagi amallari(samarasi)ni to`liq beramiz. \nUlar bunda kamsitilmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"16. Ana o`shalarga oxiratda do`zax olovidan boshqa hech vaqo yo`qdir. Bu dunyoda qilgan ishlari habata bo`ldi va qilgan amallari botil bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,142]}]}

{"text":"17. O`z Robbidan aniq hujjatga ega bo`lgan, \nunga O`sha (Robb)ning O`zidan guvoh ergashgan va \nu(guvoh)dan oldin Musoning kitobi imom va rahmat holida unga (shohid) bo`lgan kishiga(kufr keltiradilar)mi? Ana o`shalar u(shohid)ga iymon keltirurlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,247]}]}

{"text":"Guruhlardan kim unga kufr keltirsa, 
unga va'da qilingan joy jahannamdir. 
Sen u haqda shak-shubhada bo`lma! 
Albatta, u Robbingdan kelgan haqdir. 
Lekin odamlarning ko`plari iymon keltirmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,194]}]}

{"text":"18. Allohga nisbatan yolg`on to`qigan kimsadan 
ham zolimroq odam bormi? Ana o`shalar Robbilariga 
ro`baro` qilinurlar va guvohlar: Anavilar Robbilari 
sha'niga yolg`on gapirganlardir. Ogoh bo`lingkim, Allohning la'nati zolimlargadir, derlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,244]}]}

{"text":"19. Ular Allohning yo`lidan to`sarlar va \nuning egri bo`lishini xohlarlar hamda ular oxiratga \nkufr keltiruvchi kimsalardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,124]}]}

{"text":"20. Ana o`shalar yer yuzida qochib qutuluvchi bo`la olmadilar, ularga Allohdan o`zga do`st ham bo`lmadi, azob bir necha barobar qilinur. Ular eshitishga qodir \nbo`la olmadilar va ko`ra olmadilar ham.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,199]}]}

{"text":"21. Ana o`shalar o`zlariga ziyon qilganlardir va \nto`qigan narsalari ulardan g`oyib bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,91]}]}

{"text":"22. Shak-shubhasiz, albatta, ular oxiratda yana ham \nko`proq ziyon ko`rguvchilardir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,84]}]}

{"text":"23. Albatta, iymon keltirganlar, \nyaxshi amallar qilganlar va Robbilariga ishonch\n ila bo`yinsunganlar, ana o`shalar, jannat egalaridir. Ular unda abadiy qolurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"24. Bu ikki guruhning misoli xuddi karu ko`r hamda eshituvchi va ko`ruvchiga o`xshaydir. Ular bir-birlariga barobar bo`la oladilarmi? Ibrat olmaysizlarmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,154]}]}

{"text":"25. Albatta, Biz Nuhni o`z qavmiga: Albatta, men sizlarga ochiq-oydin ogohlantiruvchiman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,90]}]}

{"text":"26. Allohdan o`zgaga hech ibodat qilmanglar, \nalbatta, men sizlarga alamli kun azobi bo`lishidan \nqo`rqaman, dedirib yubordik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,127]}]}

{"text":"27. Uning qavmidan kufr keltirgan zodagonlar: \nBiz sening ham faqat o`zimizga o`xshagan odam ekaningni ko`ryapmiz, senga ichimizdan esi past pastkashlarimizgina ergashayotganini ko`ryapmiz, ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,191]}]}

{"text":"sizlarning bizdan ustun fazlingizni ko`rmayapmiz, \nbalki sizlarni yolg`onchi deb o`ylayapmiz, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,103]}]}

{"text":"28. U: Ey qavmim, ayting-chi, agar men Robbimdan aniq hujjatga ega bo`lgan bo`lsam va U menga O`z huzuridan rahmat bergan bo`lsa-yu, sizga maxfiy qolgan bo`lsa, uni sizga, agar yoqtirmasangiz ham, majburlaymizmi?! dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,221]}]}

{"text":"29. Ey qavmim, bu (da'vatim) uchun sizdan \nmol so`ramasman. Mening ajrim faqat \nAllohning zimmasida. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,102]}]}

{"text":"Men iymon keltirganlarni quvlovchi emasman. Albatta, ular Robbilariga ro`baro` bo`luvchilardir. Ammo men sizlarning johil qavm ekaningizni \nko`rmoqdaman.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,153]}]}

{"text":"30. Ey qavmim, agar ularni quvsam, \nkim menga Alloh(azobi)dan (qutulishga) \nyordam beradi? O`ylab ko`rmaysizlarmi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,114]}]}

{"text":"31. Men sizlarga: Huzurimda Allohning xazinalari bor, demasman. Faybni ham bilmasman. \nMen farishtaman, demasman. Ko`zingizga haqir \nko`rinayotganlarga Alloh hargiz yaxshilik bermas, demasman. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,199]}]}

{"text":"Ularning dillarida nima borligini Alloh yaxshi biladir. Aks holda, men, albatta, zolimlardan bo`lib qolurman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,116]}]}

{"text":"32. Ular: Ey, Nuh, batahqiq, sen biz bilan tortishding, \nko`p tortishding. Endi, agar rostgo`ylardan bo`lsang, bizga va'da qilayotgan narsangni keltir, dedilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,162]}]}

{"text":"33. U: Uni sizlarga, agar xohlasa, faqat Allohgina keltiradi va sizlar qochib qutuluvchi emassiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,98]}]}

{"text":"34. Va agar Alloh sizlarni yo`ldan ozdirishni istasa, \nmen nasihat qilishni xohlaganim bilan, nasihatim sizlarga manfaat bermas. U sizning Robbingizdir va Unga qaytarilursiz, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,181]}]}

{"text":"35. Yoki: Uni to`qib oldi, derlarmi? Agar uni to`qib olgan bo`lsam, jinoyatim o`z zimmamda va men siz qilayotgan jinoyatdan xolidirman, deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,148]}]}

{"text":"36. Va Nuhga: Qavmingdan avval iymon keltirganlardan boshqa hech kim iymon keltirmas va ularning qilmishlaridan qayg`uga tushmagin.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"37. Bizning rioyatimiz va vahiyimiz ila kema yasagin hamda zulm qilganlar to`g`risida Menga gap ochmagin, albatta, ular g`arq bo`lguvchilardir, \ndeb vahiy qildik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"38. U kema yasamoqda. O`z qavmidan bo`lgan zodagonlar qachon oldidan o`tsalar, \nuni masxara qildilar. U: Agar bizni masxara qilsangiz, biz ham xuddi siz bizni masxara qilganingizdek, \nsizni masxara qilurmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,208]}]}

{"text":"39. Bas, yaqinda kimga sharmanda qiluvchi azob kelishini va kimning ustiga muqim azob tushishini \nbilib olursiz, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,119]}]}

{"text":"40. Toki Bizning amrimiz kelib, tannur favvora otganda: U(kema)ga har narsadan bir juftdan va ahlingni ol, magar avval so`z ketganni (olma) va iymon keltirganlarni ham ol, dedik. U bilan birga iymon keltirganlar juda oz edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,226]}]}

{"text":"41. Va u: U(kema)ga mininglar, uning yurishi ham, turishi ham Allohning ismi ila bo`lur. \nAlbatta, Robbim mag`firatli va rahimlidir, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,140]}]}

{"text":"42. Va u (kema) ularni tog`lardek to`lqinda 
olib ketayotganida, Nuh bir chetda turgan o`g`liga: 
Ey o`g`lim, biz bilan birga mingin, kofirlar bilan 
birga bo`lmagin, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,174]}]}

{"text":"43. U (o`g`il): Toqqa joylashib olsam, meni suvdan saqlaydi, dedi. U esa: Bugun Allohning amridan saqlovchi yo`qdir. Magar kimni rahim qilsagina \n(saqlar), dedi. Shunda oralarini to`lqin to`sdi va u \n(o`g`il) g`arq bo`lganlardan bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,240]}]}

{"text":"44. Ey yer, suvingni yutgin, ey osmon, o`zingni tutgin, deyildi. Suv quridi. Farmon bajarildi va (kema) \nJudiy(tog`i)ga joylashdi. Hamda Zolim qavmlar \nyo`qolsin! deyildi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,175]}]}

{"text":"45. Nuh Robbiga nido qilib: Robbim, albatta, o`g`lim ahlimdandir, albatta, va'dang haqdir va Sen hukm qilguvchilarning eng hikmatlisisan, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,145]}]}

{"text":"46. U zot: Ey Nuh, albatta u ahlingdan emas. \nAlbatta, u yaxshi amal emasdir. O`zingning ilming \nbo`lmagan narsani zinhor so`ramagin. Men senga johillardan bo`lmasligingni nasihat qilaman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,196]}]}

{"text":"47. U: Robbim, men o`zimning ilmim bo`lmagan narsani Sendan so`ramoqdan panoh tilarman. \nAgar meni mag`firat qilmasang va menga rahim \nko`rsatmasang, ziyon ko`rguvchilardan bo`lurman, dedi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,191]}]}

{"text":"48. Ey Nuh, Bizdan Senga va sen bilan birga
